  "title": "Field Service Technician",
  "description": "<p>Field Service Technician</p><p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li>On-site servicing, maintenance and installation works at client's site</li><li>Repair and fault rectification on equipment</li><li>Support in preparation of equipment (before delivery) & delivery</li><li>Assisting in Service Centre activities</li><li>Ability to diagnose fault to component level</li><li>Support in-house and field service job</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year(s) experience in relevant field</li><li>Good communication, independent, committed, full of initiative, meticulous, good customer service</li><li>Entry-level are welcome but must have willing-to-learn attitude</li><li>Driving license (Class 2 and/or Class 3/4 manual)</li><li>Able to work overtime (Saturday) when required</li><li><strong>Can start work immediately</strong></li></ul><p>Benefits : Good salary package / 5 days / Incentive / AWS</p><p>Only shortlisted candidate will be notified</p><p>Interested candidate may send in your resume to: hr@puricare.com.sg or whatsapp: 96518935</p>",
